address: South Korea, Ansan-si, 경기도 안산시 상록구 성호로 113 (이동)
description: The Ansan Botanical Garden has 3 pavilions: one pavilion is a tropical garden, the second pavilion and the third pavilion both feature marsh plants. Outside there are 4 rose gardens, an orchard, a wild botanical garden, a succession of plants and a pond (46 species of plants in total, including the red Momo plant lotus). The Botanical Garden has a pyramid-shaped modern greenhouse that is the pride of Ansan City.
